\subsection ug_build_binaries Build the RMOL project
To run the configuration script the first time, go to the top
directory (where the RMOL package has been un-packed), and issue the
following command:
 - <tt>mkdir -p build && cd build && cmake ..</tt>
 - <tt>make</tt>

\note The RMOL project can either be cloned from the <a
href="http://rmol.git.sourceforge.net/git/gitweb.cgi?p=rmol/rmol;a=tree;h=refs/heads/trunk;hb=trunk">Git
Repository</a> or downloaded as a tar-ball package from the <a
href="http://sourceforge.net/project/showfiles.php?group_id=177703">Sourceforge
Web site</a>.

